{"tid":1612045,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【其實想點啫】周柏豪微博點讚何君堯10.1赴京照 網民發現後彈弓手收回","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:32:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7883b0db645de28e9df7d59c3d3693f08e25593","tid":1612045,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"昨日「黑色10.1」，克警不但用實彈近距離射向示烕者致命部位，更亂槍掃射記者，情緒失控如同入了魔道，人神共憤。惟早被白色恐怖覆蓋的娛樂圈，願意發聲的藝人依然寥可數，反而大家趁昨日10.1積極向祖國獻殷勤。<br />\n而早於數月前，因為在IG呼籲港人要登記做選民，觸發大陸網民神經被炮轟為「港獨豪」的周柏豪，昨日雖然未有更新微博，但卻被網民發現他竟然在何君堯微博、貼在北京「集郵」相的貼文點讚，引來網民關注。<br />\n周柏豪自8月26日轉載過由公司發的聲明，澄清自己並非港獨，而且熱愛祖國後，一直沒有更新微博，故網民見到他「現身」都感到驚訝，反應則有兩面，有網民表示感動，亦有人表明「唔收貨」，留言批評他︰「您配點贊何議員的微博嗎？麻煩在外網發個我是中國人再說吧！」但周柏豪最後未有聽取這位網民意見，反而把點讚取消了，未知這是算是另一種表態。<br />\n事實上，周柏豪過去多月工作仍未回復正軌，雖然在大陸音樂平台，一度被消失的歌曲已「翻生」，但風波一日未平息，工作一定受阻，就連出席香港的活動都不接受傳媒訪問，明顯不想講多錯多，早於8月更把多年來數千個貼文都刪掉，事後其經人則在個人帳號貼文籲歌迷不要擔心：「他沒事，有我在旁守護，大家乖，你們給他空間靜一靜，好嗎？Stay Positive, No Worry, Be Happy, Keep Going, Everything will be fine.（保持正面，不用擔心，開心一點，一直走下去，所有事情也會好的。）」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1569995205_5cba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1569995205_5cba.jpg&h=e4fa8a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1569995205_4c52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1569995205_4c52.jpg&h=e8ee8d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周柏豪昨日點讚何君堯這個貼文，但其後又取消。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1569995205_7a53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1569995205_7a53.jpg&h=b9533b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柏豪取消點讚前仍有fans留言表示見到他回來很滿足。（網上圖片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191002/60108278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60108278&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmvolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=1b6e1ce7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60108278&h=d9738ad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191002/60108278</a>"},{"pid":"1b116a3c6994aaf07582fe1b2b7f9ca7a8f2a2b3","tid":1612045,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"香港人會記得的"},{"pid":"1b3ab63a20957fb7a24d6ec0cec82c18dc807937","tid":1612045,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185c3130faf54efe898b98ddef957e59fd2d7c04","tid":1612045,"uid":232370,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"可能個微博唔係佢用O既呢"},{"pid":"25cfdadc4610958b2e30ec4d3468acdd815f5469","tid":1612045,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b116a3c6994aaf07582fe1b2b7f9ca7a8f2a2b3","tid":1612045,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"香港人會記得的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"第日一定要清算佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}